hwCluster.name: hwCluster
hwCluster.contactinfo: Huawei Industrial Base Bantian, Longgang Shenzhen 518129 People's Republic of China Website: http://www.huawei.com Email: support@huawei.com
hwCluster.description: HUAWEI-HGMP-MIB is defined and owned by Huawei. This MIB includes four parts: the cluster, stack, Neighbor Discovery Protocol (NDP), and Network Topology Discovery Protocol (NTDP). This MIB can monitor the cluster, stack and topology collection.

hgmpMemberfailure.name: hgmpMemberfailure
hgmpMemberfailure.description: When a cluster member failed, send an SNMP trap to the network manager.

hgmpMemberRecover.name: hgmpMemberRecover
hgmpMemberRecover.description: When a cluster member recovered, send an SNMP trap to the network manager.

hgmpMemberStatusChange.name: hgmpMemberStatusChange
hgmpMemberStatusChange.description: When a cluster member status changed, send an SNMP trap to the network manager.

hgmpNetTopChange.name: hgmpNetTopChange
hgmpNetTopChange.description: When net topology of this cluster change, send a snmp trap to the network management.

hgmpMemberAdd.name: hgmpMemberAdd
hgmpMemberAdd.description: When a cluster member added, send an SNMP trap to the network manager.

hgmpSetVLANSecurity.name: hgmpSetVLANSecurity
hgmpSetVLANSecurity.description: Configure whether to perform the VLAN check inside the cluster. The default value is noSecurity(0).

hgmpHandShakeInterval.name: hgmpHandShakeInterval
hgmpHandShakeInterval.description: Handshaking interval of the cluster member switches. The default value is 10.

hgmpHandShakeHoldtime.name: hgmpHandShakeHoldtime
hgmpHandShakeHoldtime.description: Holdtime of command switch and member switch in the cluster. The default value is 60.

hgmpGrpMemberTableChange.name: hgmpGrpMemberTableChange
hgmpGrpMemberTableChange.description: Add 1 to the member list after it changes. The administrator checks if the value has changed. If not, it will not read the list once more. The default value is 0.

hgmpMemberDisconRate.name: hgmpMemberDisconRate
hgmpMemberDisconRate.description: Disconnection times of the member and command switches divided by member number times 1000. The default value is 0.

hgmpCmdLanswitchFlag.name: hgmpCmdLanswitchFlag
hgmpCmdLanswitchFlag.description: Command switch flag. The default value is false(0). If the value is set to 1, the cluster name is 'huawei' by default.

hgmpCmdClusterName.name: hgmpCmdClusterName
hgmpCmdClusterName.description: Cluster name of the command switch.

hgmpMngPriIpSegCMIP.name: hgmpMngPriIpSegCMIP
hgmpMngPriIpSegCMIP.description: The private management IP address of the command switch, which cannot be modified after the cluster has been created. The default value is '0.0.0.0'.

hgmpMngPriIpMask.name: hgmpMngPriIpMask
hgmpMngPriIpMask.description: The private management IP address mask assigned by the command switch, which cannot be modified after the cluster has been created. The default value is '0.0.0.0'.

hgmpFtpServer.name: hgmpFtpServer
hgmpFtpServer.description: The cluster members can access the FTP Server through the command switch, which can only be configured and accessed on the command switch. The default value is '0.0.0.0'.

hgmpTftpServer.name: hgmpTftpServer
hgmpTftpServer.description: The cluster members can access the TFTP Server through the command switch, which can only be configured and accessed on the command switch. The default value is '0.0.0.0'.

hgmpSnmpHost.name: hgmpSnmpHost
hgmpSnmpHost.description: The Snmp Host to send the cluster trap packets, which can only be configured and accessed on the command switch. The default value is '0.0.0.0'.

hgmpLogHost.name: hgmpLogHost
hgmpLogHost.description: Log host of the cluster, which can only be configured and accessed on the command switch. The default value is '0.0.0.0'.

hgmpGrpMemberEntry.description: Provides information about cluster member entry.

hgmpGrpMemberDeviceId.description: 2 bytes address type of the member switch + 2 bytes /0 + MAC address, comprising a character string of hexadecimal numbers.

hgmpGrpMemberSerial.description: When adding member switch to the cluster, the command switch will assign an unique integer to identify it.

hgmpGrpMemberEnrollTime.description: Enrollment time of the member, measured in seconds.

hgmpClusterDiscAgingTime.description: Aging time of the lanswitch in disconnect state. The default value is 0.

hgmpPlugAndPlayStatus.description: Status of the plug and play function. The default value is disabled(2) .

hgmpManageVlan.description: ID of the management VLAN of the cluster. The default value is 1.

hgmpSftpServer.name: hgmpSftpServer
hgmpSftpServer.description: The cluster members can access the SFTP Server through the command switch, which can only be configured and accessed on the command switch. The default value is '0.0.0.0'.
